<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR1h0004-en-1053d4b8" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>1809, Confucius. Vol. 1 – The works of Confucius   </title><editor role="translator"> Joshua Marshman Ch. I-X</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>1809, Confucius. Vol. 1 – The works of Confucius   </title>Serampore: Printed at the Mission Press, 1809</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR1h0004"><title xml:lang="och">論語</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="en">English</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-03-20T01:08:06.842+09:00</date> by CH</creation><creation resp="#CH">Header modified: <date>2024-03-20T01:11:09.552+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR1h0004-start"><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:13:51.886+09:00">Chee says,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:14:01.311+09:00"> learn ; and continually practise~ </seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:15:00.704+09:00">Is it not delightful!</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:15:35.419+09:00">To have a friend come from a distant part.,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:15:35.796+09:00">is it not happiness?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:16:29.896+09:00">A man without knowledge and (yet) withoutenvy,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:16:30.432+09:00">is he not the honourable man ?</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:18:05.947+09:00">Yaou-chee says,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:30:50.161+09:00">that is the man, (who possessesfilial piety and fraternal respect.)  Possessing filial piety and fraternal respect, and approvingopposition to superiors,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:19:47.221+09:00">few are to be found.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:20:12.277+09:00">Ofthose who dislike opposition to superiors, and(yet) encourage insurrection;</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:20:13.624+09:00">I have found none .</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:21:19.998+09:00">The honorable man carefully regards the root.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:21:34.03+09:00">The root fixed, and the habit formed,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:21:41.195+09:00">filial pietyand fraternal respect (follow.)</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:22:02.697+09:00">These are thesource of virtue.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:22:41.506+09:00">Chee says,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:23:11.511+09:00">fair words, and a humble countenance;</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:23:12.584+09:00">little real virtue.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:26:09.908+09:00">Chung*-chee says,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:26:17.934+09:00">I daily examine myself ina threefold manner;</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:26:27.653+09:00">in my transactions with men,whether I am upright;</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:26:42.192+09:00">in my intercourse withfriends, whether I am faithful;</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:26:43.082+09:00">and whether I exemplify the instructions of my master.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:28:57.738+09:00">Chee says,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:29:23.55+09:00">in ruling the extensive province,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:30:10.869+09:00">diligently·regard business and be sincere (in yourpromises)</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:30:14.753+09:00">practise a discreet reconomy, and lovemankind :</seg><seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-07-24T16:30:21.182+09:00">employ the people in season.</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>